ORIGIN OF THIS CONFIGURATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

The setup reproduced here was inspired by the terminal workflow Kun Chen
demonstrated on video, notably in the interview published by David Ondrej
("This L8 engineer reveals his Agentic setup"), which showed Herdr driving a
sidebar of spaces and agents.

To be explicit about provenance: no source code from Kun Chen was used, copied,
or consulted. His configuration is not public, and this repository was written
from scratch by observing the resulting behaviour and then reading the WezTerm
and Herdr documentation. Any resemblance is convergence on the same tools, not
shared code. The credit owed is for the idea, and it is gladly given.
